#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.97"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.97:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:0.2"
msgid "10. Kakudhavagga "
msgstr "10. With Kakudha "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: tatiyaakuppasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.97:0.3"
msgid "97. Kathāsutta "
msgstr "97. Talk "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.121, sc1
msgctxt "an5.97:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu ānāpānassatiṃ bhāvento nacirasseva akuppaṃ paṭivijjhati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant developing mindfulness of breathing who has five things will soon penetrate the unshakable. "

msgctxt "an5.97:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appaṭṭho hoti appakicco subharo susantoso jīvitaparikkhāresu; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant has few requirements and duties, and is easily looked after and contented with life’s necessities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.4"
msgid "appāhāro hoti anodarikattaṃ anuyutto; "
msgstr "They eat little, not devoted to filling their stomach. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.5"
msgid "appamiddho hoti jāgariyaṃ anuyutto; "
msgstr "They are rarely drowsy, and are dedicated to wakefulness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.6"
msgid "yāyaṃ kathā ābhisallekhikā cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "They get to take part in talk about self-effacement that helps open the heart, when they want, without trouble or difficulty. That is, "

msgctxt "an5.97:1.7"
msgid "appicchakathā … pe … vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, evarūpiyā kathāya nikāmalābhī hoti akicchalābhī akasiralābhī; "
msgstr "talk about fewness of wishes, contentment, seclusion, keeping your distance, arousing energy, ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.8"
msgid "yathāvimuttaṃ cittaṃ paccavekkhati. "
msgstr "They review the extent of their mind’s freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.97:1.9"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu ānāpānassatiṃ bhāvento nacirasseva akuppaṃ paṭivijjhatī”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant developing mindfulness of breathing who has these five things will soon penetrate the unshakable.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.97:1.10"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

